{"tid":432230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽完施政報告，以為我去左澳門","createTime":"2017-10-11T10:40:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T11:07:22.000Z","uid":35870,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"740b76b3b86f03879777fb1515aa3aee552f8cfb","tid":432230,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T10:40:46.000Z","msg":"施政報告重點係派錢，派交通津貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你家下當澳門年年派8000呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n梁振英年代都會講下今年有幾多地賣左，土地儲備點點點，未來潛在土地供應幾多幾多<br />\n<br />\n家陣林鄭淨係講埋d乜7首置盤乜乜乜，屌你d供應咪又係咁多，只係將公屋改個名做X屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你上任前講埋d咩東大嶼都會，填海填梅窩，北區發展，而家唔撚見晒，痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁搞法，梁振英都上神枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"310bcd206c3e048833a8625c2bc5a23e0631792b","tid":432230,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T10:42:14.000Z","msg":"淨係識派錢on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都識做啦你老尾"},{"pid":"e8fc2481f24545206f3cca4c8310eaa40b6f74e6","tid":432230,"uid":35730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T10:44:31.000Z","msg":"咪係，仲要唔係派得多，多撚謝"},{"pid":"a53bbf8d72d4ac6be8579e823201cf8beddd6b6b","tid":432230,"uid":143260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T10:44:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就喺咁俾人屌先喺林鄭正職"},{"pid":"4d574180579ade08ded8405e0dbf86dede01577e","tid":432230,"uid":59919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T10:46:51.000Z","msg":"你真係派8000又唔驅"},{"pid":"6a63dc2549d15125711c09e1e5e11